{"title":"Texturelabs 拼贴纹理练习","uid":"4496cf5f1ac2aec56740fc77e8d6a4ef","slug":"CollagePractice","date":"2022-04-01T13:18:36.000Z","updated":"2022-04-16T12:14:49.192Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CollagePractice.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/16/LtZt56.png","content":"<p>使用软件：Photoshop<br>练习使用的图片是之前临摹的一张厚涂插画。此方法也可以适用一些人物画像或照片中。</p>\n<h2 id=\"拼贴图像的处理步骤\"><a href=\"#拼贴图像的处理步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"拼贴图像的处理步骤\"></a>拼贴图像的处理步骤</h2><p>首先对彩色图像进行去饱和度处理。<br>接着对图像使用油画滤镜，可以消除一些噪点上的绿色，并能有一个更平滑流动的输入。<br>再为图像增加一点 阴影/高光 默认设置即可。<br>并接下来使用木刻滤镜，并在保留原始图像的样貌的同时最大化色阶数和边缘简化度。<br>可以得到一个这样的画面。</p>\n<img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/16/LtZzL9.jpg\"  width=\"615\" height=\"948\">\n\n<p>接下来我们对这个图像做一个色阶和色调分离，使它的黑白灰更明显。</p>\n<img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/01/aBGckFsWXRxUe58.png\"  width=\"615\" height=\"948\">\n\n<p>一个非常关键的步骤，使用渐变映射将黑白灰的图像转化为黑红绿蓝，可以使拼贴不同纹理的部分分离出来。这里将渐变映射的黑色设置在100% 红色设置在33% 绿色设置在67% 蓝色设置在100%即可。</p>\n<img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/01/ra85M9pNQqIlOfk.png\"  width=\"615\" height=\"948\">\n\n<p>最后将拼贴的纹理素材贴入。将其的图层属性的“混合颜色带”中的下一图层，对应到灰红绿蓝上。<br>其中灰色的全部拉到黑这边，其余的分别拉到红绿蓝这边。</p>\n<img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/16/LtZt56.png\"  width=\"615\" height=\"948\">\n\n\n<h2 id=\"原图与拼贴后的图片对比\"><a href=\"#原图与拼贴后的图片对比\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原图与拼贴后的图片对比\"></a>原图与拼贴后的图片对比</h2><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/16/LteudI.png\"  width=\"615\" height=\"948\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/16/LtZt56.png\"  width=\"615\" height=\"948\">\n\n<p>拼贴素材来源：<a href=\"https://texturelabs.org/tutorials/collage-effect-in-photoshop\">https://texturelabs.org/tutorials/collage-effect-in-photoshop</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"使用软件：Photoshop练习使用的图片是之前临摹的一张厚涂插画。此方法也可以适用一些人物画像或照片中。 拼贴图像的处理步骤首先对彩色图像进行去饱和度处理。接着对图像使用油画滤镜，可以消除一些噪点上的绿色，并能有一个更平滑流动的输入。再为图像增加一点 阴影/高光 默认设置即可。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":485,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Practice","slug":"Practice","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Practice.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8B%BC%E8%B4%B4%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">拼贴图像的处理步骤</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%BE%E4%B8%8E%E6%8B%BC%E8%B4%B4%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94\"><span class=\"toc-text\">原图与拼贴后的图片对比</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Polaerocy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/static/img/Avatar.jpeg","link":"/","description":"A graphic designer who aims to design the whole stack","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Blender渲染练习（三） Streetscape","uid":"68c741b1082214460936da4b2b32a83d","slug":"BlenderPractice2","date":"2022-04-04T03:13:25.000Z","updated":"2022-04-04T03:17:31.087Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/BlenderPractice2.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/04/UNFHJXmVOgkGEiD.png","text":"按照CrossMind Studio的Blender入门教程查漏补缺中…发现Blender 3.0的吸附功能貌似不稳定？ 使用软件：Blender/Cycles本作品仅作为练习记录 效果图 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":95,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Practice","slug":"Practice","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Practice.json"}],"author":{"name":"Polaerocy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/static/img/Avatar.jpeg","link":"/","description":"A graphic designer who aims to design the whole stack","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"Blender渲染练习（二） MagicBook","uid":"73f6fe89eb2c14c455fd048fecc697d2","slug":"BlenderPractice1","date":"2022-03-27T12:25:36.000Z","updated":"2022-03-27T13:43:34.692Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/BlenderPractice1.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http